trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.ChildChanged"></xref> and <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.ChildChanged"></xref> events.
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 데이터를 제공는 <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.ChildChanged"> </xref> 및 <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.ChildChanged"> </xref> 이벤트입니다.

trans-unit.source: The ChildChangedEventArgs class is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> classes when the values of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=fullName> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=fullName> properties change.
trans-unit.target: ChildChangedEventArgs 클래스에서 사용 됩니다는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost>및 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost>때 클래스의 값은 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=fullName>또는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성 변경.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost.Child%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ElementHost> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.WindowsFormsHost>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs.PreviousChild%2A> property to get the previously assigned child control or element.
trans-unit.target: 사용 된 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs.PreviousChild%2A>이전에 할당 된 자식 컨트롤 또는 요소를 가져올 속성입니다.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.ChildChangedEventArgs.PreviousChild%2A>
